OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1784715503
OL,3,CBoy, 15, detained under mental health
OL,4,Cact after death of 50-year-old man
OL,6,FA 15-year-old boy has been detained
OL,7,Funder the mental health act after a
OL,8,Fmurder investigation was launched
OL,9,Ffollowing the death of a 50-year-old
OL,10,Fman.
OL,12,FGreater Manchester Police (GMP) said
OL,13,Fit received new information about the
OL,14,Fdeath of the man who was found with
OL,15,Fserious head and chest injuries at an
OL,16,Faddress on Gray Street in Bolton on 30
OL,17,FJune.
OL,19,FHe died at the scene and officers say
OL,20,Fafter new information came to light an
OL,21,Finvestigation was launched.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,370,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1784715503
OL,3,CBoy, 15, detained under mental health
OL,4,Cact after death of 50-year-old man
OL,6,FIt is believed to an isolated incident
OL,7,Fwith no wider risk to the local
OL,8,Fcommunity, the force added.
OL,10,FDetective Chief Inspector Louise
OL,11,FEdwards said: "Our thoughts remain
OL,12,Ffirmly with the man's family and
OL,13,Ffriends.
OL,15,F"Following new information coming to
OL,16,Flight regarding his death, we are now
OL,17,Fcarrying out enquiries to establish
OL,18,Fthe full circumstances surrounding the
OL,19,Fevents of the day he died.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,370,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1784715503
OL,3,CBoy, 15, detained under mental health
OL,4,Cact after death of 50-year-old man
OL,6,F"We'd like to thank members of the
OL,7,Fcommunity for their patience and
OL,8,Funderstanding as we carry out
OL,9,Fenquiries in and around the Gray
OL,10,FStreet area.
OL,12,F"There is no information to suggest
OL,13,Fthere is any wider risk to the public,
OL,14,Fand we are not seeking anyone else in
OL,15,Frelation to this incident.
OL,17,F"Anyone who has information that may
OL,18,Fassist police enquiries and who has
OL,19,Fnot yet spoken to officers is asked to
OL,20,Fcontact Greater Manchester Police on
OL,21,F101, quoting log 3965 of 30/05/26.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
